terprise discovered a spill at their west cushing tank farm in cushing oklahoma approximately  gallons of crude oil were released within the terminal a tank line had failed from internal corrosion on january   a road crew punctured the seaway s crude oil pipeline in texas which is jointly joined by enterprise products partners and the canadian enbridge inc through the joint venture seaway crude pipeline company two days later it was unclear how much oil had spilled over the nearby highway  northeast of dallas after the incident supply concerns reportedly helped push oil prices  higher in early trading to nearly  a barrel assetsedit according to the company website it has the following assets pipelinesedit  miles  km of pipelines including ngl pipelines  services  miles  km of natural gas liquids pipelines onshore natural gas pipelines  services  miles  km of natural gas pipelines onshore crude oil pipelines  services  miles  km of onshore crude oil pipelines offshore pipelines  services  miles  km of gulf of mexico natural gas and crude oil pipelines storage salt domeedit  mmbbls of ngl storage capacity × cu ft  m of natural gas storage capacity drilling platformsedit seven offshore gulf of mexico hub platforms ngl importexport terminals on the houston ship channel import unload up to  bblshr export load up to  bblshr fractionationedit  ngl and propylene fractionators ngl nine plants with a net capacity of approximately  mbpd propylene four plants with a net capacity of approximately  mbpd isomerization three plants with a net capacity of approximately  mbpd natural gas processingedit  plants with a net processing capacity of  bcfday referencesedit  a b c enterprise gp holdings names ceopermanent dead link forbes associated press july    morris mike  february  natural gas plant burns in mont belvieu houston chronicle retrieved  march    httpswwwphmsadotgovstaticfilesphmsadownloadablefilesfilespipelinefailurereportsenterpriseproductsoperatingllcfirreportandappendices